bilingual.source: The government is preparing for an imminent natural disaster.
bilingual.target: 政府正在为即将发生的自然灾害做准备。

bilingual.source: Imminent: (especially of something unpleasant) likely to happen very soon
bilingual.target: （尤指不愉快的事）即将发生的；临近的

bilingual.source: No one has given out a warning of the imminent danger.
bilingual.target: 没有人对即将发生的危险发出警告.

bilingual.source: There has been a good deal of talk in recent weeks about imminent economic armageddon.
bilingual.target: 对即将发生的世界经济末世之战,这些周里会有很多的讨论.

bilingual.source: For example, a processing computer might use the data from the image sensor to decide that a collision is imminent and send a command to the vehicle subsystems to apply brakes.
bilingual.target: 例如处理计算机可能使用来自图像传感器的数据，确定即将发生的碰撞，并向车辆子系统发出指令以采取刹车措施。

bilingual.source: The merger between the two companies is imminent.
bilingual.target: 两家公司之间的合并即将发生。

bilingual.source: The dark clouds indicate that a storm is imminent.
bilingual.target: 乌云表明暴风雨即将发生。

bilingual.source: The movie depicted a scenario where Armageddon was imminent.
bilingual.target: 这部电影描绘了一个世界末日的决战即将来临的情景。

bilingual.source: The doctor said that the birth of the baby was imminent.
bilingual.target: 医生说婴儿的出生即将发生。

bilingual.source: The company warned that layoffs were imminent due to financial losses.
bilingual.target: 公司警告说，由于财务亏损，裁员即将发生。

yingyinNormal.en: I programmed it in to warn me of an imminent system shutdown.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我编程让它在系统面临紧急关闭威胁时警示我。

yingyinNormal.en: He was being treated well and was grateful to President Petrov for granting his imminent release.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他一直得到善待，并感谢佩特罗夫总统即将批准释放他。

yingyinNormal.en: But whether that's the truth or not, this is an imminent threat which we must deal with immediately.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但无论事实是否如此，解决这个威胁迫在眉睫。

yingyinNormal.en: Every single German message, every surprise attack, every bombing run, every imminent U-boat assault. They were all floating through the air.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每一封德国电报，每一次突然袭击，每一次炸弹轰炸，每一次U艇攻击，都在空中无线传输着，都在空中无线传输着。

yingyinNormal.en: She saw me get hit by the express train. This isn't getting us anywhere. No, no, no, wait, wait. We have to send him in. A second attack is imminent, Dr. Rutledge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她看见我被一列快车压死了。事情没有任何进展。不，等等。等等，必须把他送回去。第二轮爆炸迫在眼前，拉特里奇博。

yingyinNormal.en: It is a cutting edge high-tech firm, out of the Midwest awaiting imminent patent approval on the next generation of radar detectors that have both huge military and civilian applications now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一家高科技公司，就在中西部，安若坦实业就等着新一代的的雷达探测仪专利批复下来了，在军用及民用领域都会被广泛应用。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
